    "Imposing a strict criterion for matching all entity spans in PolyIE could lead to counterintuitive evaluation outcomes.",
    "Tables 4 and 5 present the complete results of our experiments on the NER and RE tasks, respectively.",
    "Due to the limiation of computational resources, we do not conduct the full set of ablation studies on open-source LLMs or the RE task, and only validate our key point, G&O, by comparing it to the One-Step approach.",
